Dining alfresco during late summer? Sign us up! @foxmeetsbear shows us how to create an eclectic dinner table with gold cutlery, spode blue plates, a linen tablecloth, updated serveware, and chic glassware.

In her own words: "The girls and I freshened up our back deck to plan ahead for more outdoor dinners. We all dressed up and set the table with wild black walnut branches that smelled SO lush. We used our new brass silverware, lit some candles (both from Amazon!) and enjoyed baked fish, warm bread, and a fresh dandelion green salad."

Love this table scene? We've linked a few lookalikes along with links for the candles and cutlery. Head to the link in our bio and tap the image to shop! #amazonhome #founditonamazon
